main event: On July 5, 1965, a civilian reported seeing one unidentified object with a flashing red light in Xenia, Ohio.
interesting points: The observation lasted for 3 minutes,The object was seen moving east,It appeared to have a medium brightness with a fading light effect,There were 74 aircraft in and out of Wright Field and 72 from Patterson Field around the time of observation,No photographs were present in the report, only diagrams and sketches.
sighted object: one unidentified object with flashing red light
witness description: Civilian who observed the object during the sighting
